r%20dumb%20mistakes%20in%20the%20future%20is%20incredibly%20powerful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20steps%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20algorithm%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMake%20requirements%20less%20dumb%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDelete%20the%20part%20or%20process%20step%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOptimise%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccelerate%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAutomate%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20simple%20algorithm%20that%20I%20came%20up%20with%20to%20help%20me%20make%20fewer%20dumb%20mistakes%20in%20the%20future%20is%20incredibly%20powerful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtRJhe0gy6y%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtRJhe0gy6y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1862363270931255356%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalter%20Isaacson%20mentioned%20the%20algorithm%20in%20Mr%20Musk's%20biography%20and%20detailed%20each%20step.%20He%C2%A0said%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20insists%20every%20requirement%20be%20scrutinised%20and%20traced%20back%20to%20an%20individual%2C%20rather%20than%20accepting%20it%20as%20a%20directive%20from%20a%20vague%20entity%20such%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20department%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csafety%20department.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20also%20advocates%20deleting%20parts%20or%20processes%20wherever%20possible.%20He%20notes%20they%20may%20have%20to%20be%20added%20back%20later%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20people%20do%20not%20end%20up%20adding%20back%20at%20least%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20them%2C%20they%20didn't%20delete%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOptimisation%20should%20only%20come%20after%20unnecessary%20elements%20have%20been%20removed.%20Mr%20Musk%20warns%20against%20the%20common%20mistake%20of%20simplifying%20and%20optimi