f%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20choice%20for%20Secretary%20of%20Defence%2C%20accused%20him%20of%20mistreating%20women%20over%20the%20years%20and%20exhibiting%20a%20lack%20of%20moral%20character.%20The%202018%20email%2C%20made%20public%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F11%2F29%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fpete-hegseth-mother-email.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20painted%20a%20damning%20picture%20of%20his%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20behalf%20of%20all%20the%20women%20(and%20I%20know%20it's%20many)%20you%20have%20abused%20in%20some%20way%2C%20I%20say...get%20some%20help%20and%20take%20an%20honest%20look%20at%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Penelope%20Hegseth%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20an%20abuser%20of%20women%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20the%20ugly%20truth%20and%20I%20have%20no%20respect%20for%20any%20man%20that%20belittles%2C%20lies%2C%20cheats%2C%20sleeps%20around%2C%20and%20uses%20women%20for%20his%20power%20and%20ego.%20You%20are%20that%20man%20(and%20have%20been%20for%20years)%20and%20as%20your%20mother%2C%20it%20pains%20me%20and%20embarrasses%20me%20to%20say%20that%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20sad%2C%20sad%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPenelope%20Hegseth%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20she%20later%20sent%20an%20apologetic%20follow-up%20to%20Pete.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fired%20off%20that%20original%20email%20in%20anger%2C%20with%20emotion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20attributing%20the%20tone%20to%20the%20difficult%20circumstances%20surrounding%20her%20son's%20divorce%20from%20his%20second%20wife%2C%20Samantha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20email's%20tone%20was%20scathing%20as%20Penelope%20criticised%20Pete%20for%20his%20treatment%20of%20Samantha.%20She%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20tried%20to%20keep%20quiet%20about%20your%20character%20and%20behaviour%2C%20but%20after%20listening%20to%20the%20way%20you%20made%20Samantha%20feel%20today%2C%20I%20cannot%20stay%20silent.%20And%20as%20a%20woman%20and%20your%20mother%20I%20feel%20I%20must%20speak%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CSam%20is%20a%20good%20mother%20and%20a%20good%20person%20(under%20the%20circumstances%20that%20you%20created)%20and%20I%20know%20deep%20down%20you%20know%20that.%20For%20you%20to%20try%20to%20label%20her%20as%20%E2%80%98unstable'%20for%20your%20own%20advantage%20is%20despicable%20and%20abusive.%20Is%20there%20any%20sense%20of%20decency%20left%20in%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%2C%20she%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20still%20love%20you%2C%20but%20we%20are%20broken%20by%20your%20behaviour%20and%20lack%20of%20character.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20a%20former%20Fox%20News%20contributor%20and%20veteran%20of%20the%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20wars%2C%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in%20controversy%20following%20Trump's%20nomination.%20The%20accusations%20in%20the%20email%20are%20particularly%20significant%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Hegseth's%20anticipated%20Senate%20confirmation%20hearings%2C%20where%20his%20character%20will%20be%20closely%20scrutinised.%20Reports%20of%20infidelity%20and%20a%20rape%20complaint%20dating%20back%20to%202017%2C%20which%20was%20not%20pursued%20by%20authorities%2C%20have%20already%20attracted%20attention%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20Hegseth%20has%20maintained%20the%20complaint%20was%20a%20false%20accusation%20by%20a%20woman%20he%20had%20a%20consensual%20relationship%20with%20and%20reportedly%20paid%20a%20settlement%20to%20protect%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Hegseth%20was%20navigating%20an%20acrimonious%20divorce%20process.%20Samantha%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20three%20of%20his%20children%2C%20filed%20for%20divorce%20after%20discovering%20Pete%20had%20fathered%20a%20child%20with%20Jennifer%20Rauchet%2C%20a%20colleague%20at%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20email%2C%20Steven%20Cheung%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20President-elect%20Trump%2C%20accused%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20of%20releasing%20%E2%80%9Can%20out-of-context%20snippet%E2%80%9D%20and%20emphasised%20that%20Penelope%20Hegseth%20had%20apologised%20for%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20couple's%20divorce%2C%20which%20was%20finalised%20in%202019%2C%20included%20disputes%20over%20parenting%20time%20that%20required%20court-appointed%20mediation.%20Pete%20Hegseth%20later%20stated%20that%20he%20regretted%20derogatory%20texts%20sent%20to%20Samantha%2C%20pledging%20to%20communicate%20more%20respectfully%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732949160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fs80c8g9_pete-hegseth-afp_625x300_17_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-s-defence-secretary-pick-pete-hegseth-accused-of-abuse-by-mother-in-2018-email-7138953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20pick%20for%20defence%20secretary%2C%20faces%20accusations%20from%20his%20mother%20of%20a%20'lack%20of%20character'%20due%20to%20his%20behaviour%20towards%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-s-defence-secretary-pick-pete-hegseth-accused-of-abuse-by-mother-in-2018-email-7138953%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20questions%20how%20TMC%20leader's%20husband%20got%20hold%20of%20nuclear%20material%2C%20DRDO%20documents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732948867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115833080%2Cimgsize-1167178.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.in