Fus%2Fsame-sex-couple-jd-vance-trolled-for-depicting-himself-as-donald-trumps-trad-wife%2Farticleshow%2F115832529.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What's%20Happening%20in%20Syria%2C%20How%20It%20Could%20Affect%20Middle%20East%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Syria%20had%20thawed.%20But%2013%20years%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20humanitarian%20crises%20of%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20a%20new%20surge%20in%20violence%20has%20reignited%20attention%20on%20a%20conflict%20that%20had%20faded%20from%20the%20world's%20headlines.%20Syrian%20rebel%20forces%20have%20launched%20a%20major%20offensive%20on%20Aleppo%2C%20Syria's%20once-thriving%20commercial%20hub%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20challenge%20to%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad's%20regime%20in%20years%2C%20potentially%20destabilising%20an%20already%20destabilised%20Middle%20East.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Aleppo%20Matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAleppo%2C%20roughly%20350%20km%20north%20of%20the%20capital%20Damascus%2C%20has%20been%20a%20critical%20battleground%20in%20the%20Syrian%20civil%20war.%20Before%20the%20conflict%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20Syria's%20largest%20cities%2C%20home%20to%202.3%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20rebel%20forces%20seized%20the%20eastern%20half%20of%20Aleppo%2C%20making%20it%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20rebellion%20against%20President%20Assad.%20However%2C%20the%20balance%20shifted%20in%202016%20when%20Syrian%20government%20forces%2C%20backed%20by%20a%20brutal%20Russian%20aerial%20campaign%2C%20recaptured%20the%20city.%20The%20siege%20of%20Aleppo%20became%20symbolic%2C%20marked%20by%20indiscriminate%20bombings%2C%20starvation%20tactics%2C%20and%20massive%20displacement.%20By%20retaking%20Aleppo%2C%20Assad%20solidified%20his%20hold%20over%20key%20territories%2C%20bolstered%20by%20Russian%20and%20Iranian%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F0ck731bg_syria-reuters-_625x300_30_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Reuters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebel%20offensive%20has%20targeted%20areas%20surrounding%20Aleppo%20and%20advanced%20toward%20its%20outskirts.%20If%20rebels%20succeed%20in%20breaking%20through%2C%20it%20could%20put%20a%20spanner%20in%20Assad's%20control%20over%20the%20crisis-hit%20country%20and%20reignite%20intense%20urban%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Actors%20Behind%20The%20Offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20force%20leading%20the%20charge%20is%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS).%20Once%20affiliated%20with%20terror%20group%20al-Qaida%2C%20HTS%20has%20rebranded%20itself%20over%20the%20years%2C%20claiming%20to%20focus%20on%20governance%20and%20military%20strategy%20in%20opposition-held%20territories.%20While%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20continue%20to%20designate%20HTS%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20its%20leader%2C%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Golani%2C%20has%20sought%20to%20distance%20the%20group%20from%20its%20extremist%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fu3ptikeg_syria-reuters-_625x300_30_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Reuters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHTS's%20transformation%20includes%20efforts%20to%20promote%20civilian%20governance%20in%20areas%20it%20controls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20limited%20outreach%20to%20religious%20minorities.%20Despite%20these%20changes%2C%20the%20group%20maintains%20a%20controversial%20reputation%2C%20accused%20of%20harbouring%20extremist%20elements%20and%20tolerating%20militant%20activities%20within%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHTS%20is%20joined%20by%20several%20Turkish-backed%20factions%2C%20operating%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20the%20Syrian%20National%20Army.%20These%20groups%20have%20long%20had%20a%20complex%20relationship%2C%20often%20fighting%20among%20themselves%20despite%20their%20shared%20opposition%20to%20Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EObjectives%20Of%20The%20Rebel%20Offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20statement%20announcing%20the%20campaign%2C%20rebel%20military%20commander%20Lt.%20Col.%20Hassan%20Abdulghany%20described%20the%20operation%20as%20a%20defensive%20necessity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20push%20back%20their%20fire%20from%20our%20people%2C%20this%20operation%20is%20not%20a%20choice.%20It%20is%20an%20obligation%20to%20defend%20our%20people%20and%20their%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20clear%20to%20everyone%20that%20the%20regime%20militias%20and%20their%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20Iranian%20mercenaries%2C%20have%20declared%20an%20open%20war%20on%20the%20Syrian%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebels'%20immediate%20goals%20include%20halting%20airstrikes%20on%20civilian%20areas%2C%20reclaiming%20territory%2C%20and%20cutting%20off%20critical%20supply%20routes%20for%20government%20forces.%20Their%20progress%20so%20far%20has%20been%20rapid%2C%20capturing%20several%20villages%2C%20strategic%20highway%20interchanges%2C%20and%20military%20bases%20in%20Aleppo%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Assad%20Regime's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyrian%20state%20media%20has%20reported%20fierce%20resistance%20by%20government%20forces%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20inf