20in%20connection%20with%20the%20November%2024%20violence%20for%20allegedly%20committing%20%26quot%3Bprovocative%20acts%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMLAs%20Kamal%20Akhtar%2C%20Ravidas%20Mehrotra%2C%20Nawab%20Iqbal%20Mahmood%20and%20Pinky%20Singh%20Yadav%20will%20also%20be%20part%20of%20the%20delegation%2C%20the%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20had%20earlier%20postponed%20the%20proposed%20visit%20of%20its%20delegation%20after%20getting%20assurance%20from%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20of%20a%20fair%20investigation%20into%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandey%20had%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20last%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20supposed%20to%20leave%20for%20Sambhal%20at%2010%20am%20today%2C%20but%20in%20the%20meantime%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police.%20We%20told%20him%20that%20our%20people%20are%20being%20framed%2C%20even%20FIRs%20have%20been%20lodged%20against%20those%20who%20were%20not%20present%20there.%26quot%3B%20Pandey%20said%20the%20DGP%20assured%20him%20of%20a%20fair%20investigation%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20visit%20Sambhal%20after%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%20state%20president%20Ajay%20Rai%20told%20PTI%20that%20a%20party%20delegation%20will%20go%20there%20on%20December%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Sambhal%20has%20been%20tense%20since%20the%20first%20survey%20of%20the%20city's%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20conducted%20on%20November%2019%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20a%20local%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20has%20claimed%20that%20Jama%20Masjid%20stands%20on%20a%20previous%20Harihar%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20erupted%20earlier%20on%20November%2024%20as%20the%20protesters%20gathered%20near%20the%20mosque%20and%20clashed%20with%20security%20personnel%2C%20leading%20to%20stone%20pelting%20and%20arson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20people%20died%20and%20several%20others%2C%20including%20policemen%2C%20were