s-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fchennai-based-real-estate-firm-dra-to-expand-footprint-to-pune-bengaluru-124113000182_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Must%20Ensure%20Fair%20Trial%20For%20Hindu%20Monk%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Friday%20said%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh%20must%20live%20up%20to%20its%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20all%20minorities%20as%20it%20expressed%20serious%20concern%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurge%26quot%3B%20of%20extremist%20rhetoric%20and%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20temples%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20also%20hoped%20that%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20Hindu%20monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20arrested%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20sedition%20charge%2C%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20a%20just%2C%20fair%20and%20transparent%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20told%20Parliament%20that%20India%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20note%20of%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20that%20it%20is%20the%20primary%20responsibility%20of%20Dhaka%20to%20protect%20the%20life%20and%20liberty%20of%20all%20the%20citizens%2C%20including%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20come%20under%20strain%20after%20the%20interim%20government%20headed%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20came%20to%20power%20following%20the%20resignation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20in%20August%20amid%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20expressing%20concern%20over%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Hindus%2C%20in%20that%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20responsibility%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20life%20and%20liberty%20of%20all%20citizens%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20including%20minorities%2C%20rests%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Dhaka%20continues%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20related%20to%20minorities%20in%20that%20country%20%26quot%3Bclosely%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20called%20upon%20Bangladesh%20to%20take%20all%20steps%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%20and%20hoped%20that%20the%20case%20involving%20arrested%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20a%20just%2C%20fair%20and%20transparent%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20India%20has%20consistently%20and%20strongly%20raised%20with%20the%20Bangladeshi%20government%20the%20threats%20and%20targeted%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities.%20%26quot%3BOur%20position%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20very%20clear%20--%20the%20interim%20government%20must%20live%20up%20to%20its%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20all%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said%20at%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20concerned%20at%20the%20surge%20of%20extremist%20rhetoric%2C%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20provocation.%20These%20developments%20cannot%20be%20dismissed%20only%20as%20media%20exaggeration.%20We%20once%20again%20call%20upon%20Bangladesh%20to%20take%20all%20steps%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20is%20concerned%20over%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20their%20homes%20and%20business%20establishments%20and%20attacks%20on%20temples%20and%20religious%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20serious%20note%20of%20these%20incidents%20and%20shared%20its%20concerns%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Bangladesh.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BReports%20of%20attacks%20on%20temples%20and%20puja%20mandaps%20also%20came%20to%20light%20during%20the%20recent%20Durga%20Puja%20festival%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20government%20had%20expressed%20its%20serious%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20puja%20mandap%20in%20Tantibazar%2C%20Dhaka%20and%20theft%20at%20the%20Jeshoreshwari%20Kali%20temple%20at%20Satkhira%20during%20Durga%20Puja%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20said%20that%20following%20these%20attacks%20the%20Bangladeshi%20government%20had%20issued%20instructions%20for%20providing%20special%20security%20including%20deployment%20of%20Army%20and%20border%20guards%20to%20ensure%20a%20peaceful%20Durga%20Puja%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20arrest%20of%20Das%2C%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20ISKCON%20(International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness)%2C%20Jaiswal%20said%20it%20is%20India's%20expectation%20that%20a%20fair%20and%20transparent%20trial%20will%20be%20ensured%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20ISKCON%20as%20a%20globally%20well-regarded%20organisation%20with%20a%20strong%20record%20of%20social%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20said%20India%20has%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20legal%20processes%20in%20the%20case%20are%20underway.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20and%20expect%20that%20these%20processes%20will%20deal%20with%20the%20case%20in%20a%20just%2C%20fair%20and%20transparent%20manner%2C%20ensuring%20full%20respect%20for%20the%20legal%20rights%20of%20all%20concerned.%26quot%3B%20Das%20was%20arrested%20at%20Dhaka's%20Hazrat%20Shahjalal%20International%20Airport%20on%20Monday%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20sedition%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20expectation%20that%20he%20will%20get%20a%20fair%20and%20transparent%20trial%20and%20his%20legal%20rights%20will%20be%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said.%