li%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecades-long%20campaign%20of%20fraud%20and%20deception%20about%20the%20recyclability%20of%20plastics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Kansas%20county%20has%20sued%20a%20group%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20companies%2C%20including%20energy%20giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-lower-gas-prices-exxonmobil-ceo-oil-boom-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExxonMobil%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchevron-placed-on-positive-catalyst-watch-at-citi-1034066050%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChevron%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20representations%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20public%20regarding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmit-research-andrew-mcafee-says-recycling-is-useless-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecyclability%20of%20plastics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20about%20Defendants'%20profit-driven%20decision%20to%20promote%20the%20idea%20to%20the%20American%20consumer%20that%20plastics%20were%20recyclable%20and%20better%20for%20the%20environment%2C%20when%20in%20reality%20they%20had%20information%20that%20only%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20plastics%20are%20ever%20recycled%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20filed%20this%20week%20by%20Kansas'%20Ford%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Kansas%2C%20alleges%20that%20the%20petrochemical%20companies'%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20representations%26quot%3B%20around%20the%20recyclability%20of%20plastics%20has%20resulted%20in%20higher%20production%20levels%20of%20plastic%20products%2C%20more%20demand%20for%20them%2C%20inflated%20prices%20for%20plastic%20products%20as%20well%20as%20issues%20with%20plastic%20waste%20remediation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alle