ta%20shows%20employees%20who%20choose%20where%20to%20work%20are%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20workers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20side%20gigs%20than%20their%20office-based%20peers%20%E2%80%94%2034%25%20versus%2029%25%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Flinkedin-news_who-has-enough-time-for-a-side-hustle-about-activity-7267563681335382017-O2UR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20Workforce%20Confidence%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%208%2C606%20US%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20toward%20additional%20income%20streams%20appears%20strongest%20among%20those%20with%20flexible%20work%20arrangements.%20While%20only%20a%20quarter%20of%20full-time%20employees%20reported%20having%20a%20side%20gig%2C%20the%20number%20jumps%20to%2052%25%20for%20freelancers%20and%2046%25%20for%20both%20contractors%20and%20self-employed%20workers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESide%20gigs%20include%20working%20as%20consultants%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-drivers-starting-own-ride-businesses-as-earnings-drop-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erideshare%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20rental%20property%20managers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20workers'%20higher%20participation%20in%20side%20hustles%20could%20stem%20from%20increased%20time%20savings%20from%20not%20commuting.%20GPS%20data%20from%20traffic%20analytics%20company%20INRIX%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-americans-super-commuting-75-miles-work-wfh-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercommuting%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20traveling%20over%2075%20miles%20to%20work%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20same%20trend%20applies%20to%20commutes%20over%2040%20miles%20for%20the%20country's%2010%20largest%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20higher%20rate%20of%20side%20gigs%20among%20remote%20workers%2C%20though%20small%2C%20could%20also%20stem%20from%20some%20evidence%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-wfh-productivity-impact-no-consensus-goldman-sachs-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20slows%20when%20workers%20are%20pushed%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20cited%20a%20May%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greatplacetowork.com%2Fpress-releases%2Fresearch-employees-who-can-choose-between-onsite%2C-remote%2C-or-hybrid-work-are-14x-less-likely-to-%25E2%2580%2598quit-and-stay%25E2%2580%2599%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreat%20Place%20to%20Work%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20of%204%2C400%20US%20employees%2C%20which%20found%20that%20workers%20who%20could%20choose%20where%20they%20work%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20exceed%20expectations%20and%20have%20better%20relationships%20with%20their%20bosses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fopub%2Fbtn%2Fvolume-13%2Fremote-work-productivity.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20complicated%2C%20as%20various%20remote%20work%20studies%20have%20different%20conclusions.%20Stanford%20economists%20found%2010%25%20lower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsiepr.stanford.edu%2Fpublications%2Fworking-paper%2Fevolution-working-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20fully%20remote%20work%20compared%20to%20fully%20in-person%20work.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20separate%20Stanford%20report%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.stanford.edu%2Fstories%2F2024%2F06%2Fhybrid-work-is-a-win-win-win-for-companies-workers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20no%20effect%20on%20productivity%20or%20career%20advancement%20compared%20to%20in-person%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20employees%20with%20side%20hustles%2