20Foreign%20Students%20To%20Return%20Ahead%20Of%20Trump's%20Swearing-In%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeveral%20American%20universities%20have%20issued%20travel%20advisories%20for%20their%20international%20students%20as%20well%20as%20staff%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US%20before%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration%20in%20January%20next%20year%20amid%20concerns%20over%20travel%20bans%20that%20may%20be%20enacted%20by%20his%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20will%20take%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20on%20January%2020%20and%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20sign%20several%20executive%20orders%20on%20issues%20of%20economy%20and%20immigration%20on%20his%20first%20day%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20concerns%20over%20the%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20travel%20bans%20during%20his%20first%20term%20as%20president%2C%20several%20top%20US%20universities%20are%20issuing%20travel%20advisories%20for%20their%20international%20students%20and%20faculty%20who%20may%20be%20travelling%20outside%20the%20country%20around%20Trump's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20Bureau%20of%20Educational%20and%20Cultural%20Affairs%2C%20and%20the%20Institute%20of%20International%20Education%2C%20India%20and%20China%20made%20up%20over%20half%20(54%20per%20cent)%20of%20all%20international%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202009%2C%20India%20became%20the%20leading%20place%20of%20origin%20with%20331%2C602%20international%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%202023%2F2024%2C%20reflecting%20a%2023%20per%20cent%20increase%20from%20the%20prior%20year%2C%20surpassing%20China%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20'Open%20Doors%202024%20Report%20on%20International%20Educational%20Exchange'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20was%20the%20second%20leading%20place%20of%20origin%2C%20despite%20a%204%20per%20cent%20decline%20to%20277%2C398%20students.%20It%20remained%20the%20top-sending%20country%20for%20undergraduates%20and%20non-degree%20students%2C%20sending%2087%2C551%20and%205%2C517%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssociate%20Dean%20and%20Director%20at%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%20International%20Students%20Office%20David%20Elwell%20in%20a%20post%20following%20the%20presidential%20elections%20said%20that%20with%20every%20election%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20there%20is%20a%20change%20in%20administration%20on%20the%20federal%20level%20there%20can%20be%20changes%20in%20policies%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20legislation%20that%20impacts%20higher%20education%20as%20well%20as%20immigration%20and%20visa%20status%20matters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElwell%20urged%20students%20to%20assess%20their%20travel%20plans%20over%20the%20upcoming%20winter%20break%2C%20noting%20that%20new%20executive%20orders%20under%20Trump%20may%20impact%20travel%20and%20visa%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20election%20transitions%20also%20impact%20staffing%20levels%20at%20US%20Embassies%2FConsulates%20abroad%2C%20which%20could%20impact%20entry%20visa%20processing%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudents%20who%20would%20need%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20new%20entry%20visa%20at%20the%20US%20Embassy%2FConsulate%20abroad%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US%20in%20their%20student%20status%20should%20assess%20the%20possibility%20of%20facing%20any%20extensive%20processing%20times%20and%20have%20a%20backup%20plan%20if%20they%20must%20travel%20abroad%20and%20wait%20for%20a%20new%20entry%20visa%20to%20be%20issued.%20Any%20processing%20delays%20could%20impact%20students'%20ability%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US%20as%20planned%2C%26quot%3B%20Elwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Global%20Affairs%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Massachusetts%2C%20Amherst%2C%20in%20an%20advisory%20recommended%20that%20its%20%26quot%3Binternational%20community--%20including%20all%20international%20students%2C%20scholars%2C%20faculty%20and%20staff%20under%20UMass%20immigration%20sponsorship%26quot%3B%20strongly%20consider%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20before%20the%20presidential%20inauguration%20if%20they%20are%20planning%20on%20travelling%20internationally%20during%20the%20winter%20holiday%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20noting%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20requirement%20or%20mandate%20from%20UMass%2C%20nor%20was%20it%20based%20on%20any%20current%20US%20government%20policy%20or%20recommendation%2C%20the%20university%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20that%20a%20new%20presidential%20administration%20can%20enact%20new%20policies%20on%20their%20first%20day%20in%20office%20(January%2020)%20and%20based%20on%20previous%20experience%20with%20travel%20bans%20that%20were%20enacted%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20in%202017%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20Global%20Affairs%20is%20making%20this%20advisory%20out%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%20to%20hopefully%20prevent%20any%20possible%20travel%20disruption%20to%20members%20of%20our%20international%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20able%20to%20speculate%20on%20what%20a%20travel%20ban%20will%20look%20like%20if%20enacted%2C%20nor%20can%20we%20speculate%20on%20what%20particular%20countries%20or%20regions%20of%20the%20world%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20affected.%26quot%3B%20The%20Wesleyan%20Argus%2C%20the%20college%20newspaper%20of%20Wesleyan%20University%2C%20said%20in%20a%20report%20that%20the%20university%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bevaluating%20the%20potential%20future%20impacts%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20international%20and%20undocumented%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMuch%20uncertainty%20surrounds%20the%20possible%20changes%20to%20American%20immigration%20policy%20that%20could%20be%20enacted%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20beginning%20January%2020%2C%202025.%26quot%3B%20The%20report%20added%20that%20Wesleyan's%20Office%20of%20International%20Student%20Affairs%20(OISA)%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bconcerned%20about%20sweeping%20policy%20changes%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20be%20implemented%20soon%20after%20Trump's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20presidential%20inauguration%20happening%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%2020%2C%202025%2C%20and%20uncertainties%20around%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20plans%20for%20immigration-related%20policy%2C%20the%20safest%20way%20to%20avoid%20difficulty%20re-entering%20the%20country%20is%20to%20be%20physically%20present%20in%20the%20US%20on%20January%2019%20and%20the%20days%20thereafter%20of%20the%20spring%20semester%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20email%20sent%20on%20November%2018%20to%20international%20students%20studying%20under%20the%20F-1%20visa%20read%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Wesleyan%20Argus%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%20of%20his%20first%20term%20as%20president%2C%20Trump%20had%20in%20January%202017%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20banning%20nationals%20of%20seven%20Muslim-majority%20countries%20-%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%2C%20Iran%2C%20Libya%2C%20Somalia%2C%20Sudan%20and%20Yemen%20-%20from%20entering%20the%20US%20for%2090%20days%2C%20causing%20massive%20disruptions%20among%20communities%20and%20outrage%20and%20concerns%20by%20civil%20rights%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732931760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F6qubbcj_donald-trump_625x300_27_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-colleges-urge-foreign-students-to-return-to-campus-ahead-of-trumps-swearing-in-7136522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20American%20universities%20have%20issued%20travel%20advisories%20for%20