g%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22579%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinancial%20planner%20Don%20Grant.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Don%20Grant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%2020%20years%20in%20the%20business%2C%20financial%20planner%20Don%20Grant%20says%20clients%20hate%20to%20hear%20three%20things.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFirst%2C%20you're%20not%20saving%20enough%2C%20either%20for%20retirement%20or%20your%20kid's%20education.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAlso%2C%20you%20can't%20afford%20that%20much%20house%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20take%20on%20more%20investment%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDon%20Grant%20has%20been%20a%20financial%20planner%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%2C%20which%20means%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20he's%20been%20having%20tough%20talks%20with%20people%20about%20their%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20meet%20with%20clients%2C%20I%20say%2C%20I'm%20often%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20things%20that%20you%20may%20not%20want%20to%20hear%20but%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20an%20ambassador%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfp.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECFP%20Board%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20in%202021%20and%20shared%20the%20top%20three%20pieces%20of%20money%20advice%20his%20clients%20never%20want%20to%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You're%20not%20saving%20enough%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrant%20works%20with%20clients%20at%20various%20life%20stages%2C%20and%20those%20nearing%20retirement%20age%20aren't%20happy%20to%20hear%20that%20they%20can't%20leave%20their%20jobs%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20want.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20had%20to%20bend%20a%20couple%20of%20people%20back%20to%20work%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20investment%20advisor%20with%20Fortis%20Advisors%20in%20Wichita%2C%20Kansas.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20not%20putting%20away%20enough%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20hit%20our%20targets%2C%20which%20means%20you%20could%20potentially%20outlive%20your%20savings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20financial%20planner%20can%20help%20you%20examine%20your%20income%20and%20assets%20as%20well%20as%20what%20you'll%20need%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fretirement%5C%22%3Eretirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20determine%20how%20much%20you%20should%20be%20saving%20and%20investing%20to%20maintain%20your%20lifestyle%20long%20after%20you've%20put%20in%20your%20papers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20children%2C%20you%20also%20need%20to%20save%20money%20for%20their%20education%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20brilliant%20you%20think%20your%20kids%20are%2C%20said%20Grant%20(but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20saving%20enough%20for%20your%20own%20retirement).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSusie%20is%20a%20great%20tennis%20player%2C%20but%20you%20still%20need%20to%20save%20for%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20had%20a%20number%20of%20clients%20who%20have%20kids%20who%20are%20extremely%20talented%20athletes%20or%20great%20at%20academics%20and%20they%20think%20we're%20just%20going%20to%20get%20by%20on%20scholarships.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20again%20%E2%80%94%20and%20start%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-a-529-plan%5C%22%3E529%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Grant%20recommends%20saving%20about%2060%25%20of%20what%20you%20think%20your%20child's%20college%20tuition%20will%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20need%20to%20take%20on%20more%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20cash%20out%20your%20investments%20when%20the%20markets%20are%20down%2C%20but%20don't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssentially%2C%20one%20out%20of%20every%20four%20years%20the%20markets%20are%20down%2C%20but%20the%20average%20recovery%20from%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%20is%20about%20400%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20stay%20the%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20to%20trust%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Faverage-stock-market-return%5C%22%3Ehistory%20of%20the%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20markets%20we're%20invested%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%20And%20trust%20that%20your%20advisor%20has%20helped%20you%20invest%20wisely%20so%20you%20won't%20end%20up%20broke.%20%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20stay%20invested%20and%20they%20need%20to%20take%20on%20the%20risk%20to%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20their%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20this%20risk%20means%20being%20willing%20to%20stretch%20their%20investments%20beyond%20their%20own%20companies.%20Because%20entrepreneurs%20are%20already%20taking%20on%20risks%20simply%20by%20being%20in%20business%2C%20they're%20often%20leery%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20give%20me%20money%2C%20they%20want%20to%20put%20it%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwho-has-the-best-cd-rates-right-now%5C%22%3ECDs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%20But%20the%20pandemic%20showed%20why%20it's%20crucial%20for%20entrepreneurs%20to%20diversify%20their%20investments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmall%20businesses%20got%20hit%20the%20hardest%20last%20year%2C%20and%20if%20there%20is%20a%20slow%20year%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20hit%20some%20investments%20you%20had%20in%20another%20place%20that%20did%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20can't%20afford%20that%20much%20house%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20looking%20to%20buy%20your%20first%20home%20or%20your%20dream%20house%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20the%20only%20price%20tag%20you%20need%20to%20consider.%20Homeownership%20can%20be%20a%20great%20source%20of%20pride.%20But%20when%20you're%20spending%20your%20weekends%20fixing%20the%20deck%2C%20stopping%20leaks%2C%20mowing%20the%20lawn%2C%20or%20getting%20a%20new%20roof%2C%20you%20realize%20it%20also%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20your%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20asset%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20creating%20any%20income%20for%20you.%20It's%20a%20drain%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Grant%20still%20believes%20homeownership%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%20he%20asks%20his%20clients%20to%20remember%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BExamining%20how%20much%20house%20you%20can%20afford%20has%20to%20do%20with%20all%20of%20the%20management%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20house%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20Grant%20wants%20his%20clients%20to%20keep%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20to%20keeping%20on%20top%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20have%20a%20plan%2C%20monitor%20that%20plan%2C%20and%20base%20your%20spending%20on%20what%20that%20plan%20tells%20you%20that%20you%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetirement%20Planning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-robo-advisors%5C%22%3Ebest%20robo%20advisors%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20start%20your%20retirement%20planning%20journey.%20Institutions%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Frobinhood-investing-review%5C%22%3E%20Robinhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fsofi-invest-