20the%20city%20have%20lowered%20the%20levels%20of%20particulate%20matter%20and%20made%20it%20more%20livable%20and%20sustainable.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20strategies%20in%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20air%20pollution%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98superblock%E2%80%99%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20urban%20planning%20approach%20divides%20city%20streets%20into%20octagonal%20blocks.%20Inside%20these%20blocks%2C%20only%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381023%2Fbhubaneswar-odisha-best-public-transport-india-crut-sustainable-urban-mobility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20transport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20allowed%2C%20while%20cars%20can%20only%20use%20the%20outer%20streets.%20This%20reduces%20traffic%2C%20lowers%20vehicle%20emissions%2C%20and%20improves%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Barcelona%20showcasing%20its%20superblocks%2C%20with%20green%20spaces%20and%20pedestrian-friendly%20streets%20within%20the%20octagonal%20city%20blocks.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-300x146.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-500x244.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-768x374.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-150x73.jpg%20150w%5C