%20the%20group%2C%20and%20they%20pay%20Rs%20365%20every%20year%20for%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20helped%20us%20raise%20funds%20for%20plantation%20efforts%2C%20filling%20up%20watering%20holes%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299651%2Fconservationist-meera-chandran-quit-job-to-fight-invasive-plant-species-restore-forest-land%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoval%20of%20invasive%20species.%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20Sharvan%20has%20made%20smart%20use%20of%20social%20media%20to%20amplify%20his%20cause%20and%20engage%20with%20a%20larger%20audience.%20His%20Instagram%20page%2C%20%E2%80%98Thar%20Desert%20Photography%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20become%20a%20platform%20for%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20issues%20facing%20wildlife%20in%20the%20region.%20Through%20this%2C%20he%20has%20successfully%20used%20hashtags%20like%20%23HiranBachao%2C%20%23SaveRiverJojri%2C%20and%20%23GodavarBachao%20to%20attract%20attention%20to%20his%20cause%2C%20even%20getting%20%23SaveRiverJojri%20to%20trend%20number%20one%20on%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20eyes%20we%20have%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20it%20is%20that%20someone%20will%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20recently%20passed%20Wildlife%20Week%2C%20they%20carried%20out%20a%20campaign%20where%20they%20made%20frames%20of%20various%20wild%20animals%20and%20plants%20and%20presented%20them%20to%20school%20classrooms%2C%20panchayat%20houses%2C%20and%20government%20offices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20go%20to%20schools%20and%20ask%20the%20children%20%E2%80%98what%20is%20wildlife%E2%80%99%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20say%20it%E2%