bly%20an%20aftermath%20of%20some%20function.%20For%20a%20moment%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20live%20in%20India%20anymore.%20But%20the%20very%20next%20moment%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20am%20I%20being%20a%20critic%20like%20every%20other%20person%3F%E2%80%99%20With%20just%20a%20slight%20shift%20in%20perspective%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20waste%20floating%20around%2C%20but%20ideas%20and%20opportunities%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20caught%20and%20worked%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERoping%20in%20%3Cem%3EKabadi%20wallas%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20new%20vision%2C%20Rishabh%20dialled%20Nitin.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20and%20I%20have%20always%20had%20complimentary%20qualities.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20something%2C%20and%20he%20was%20immediately%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rishabh.%20The%20two%20soon%20became%20partners%20in%20a%20venture%20that%20would%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20skill%20and%20passion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20around%20just%20looking%20at%20dumpyards%20and%20the%20heaps%20of%20trash%20that%20was%20piled%20up%20there%2C%20either%20waiting%20to%20be%20burnt%20or%20to%20end%20up%20in%20a%20landfill%20for%20life%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289075%2Fisb-grad-helps-large-fmcg-brands-recycle-plastic-packaging-reduce-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20was%20the%20biggest%20culprit%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nitin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%20of%20research%2C%20compliance%20checks%2C%20and%20operational%20planning%2C%20the%20two%20friends%20registered%20their%20company%2C%20%E