tion-groundwater-recharge%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20groundwater%20recharge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20helping%20to%20keep%20roads%20dry%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECommunity%20engagement%20and%20social%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20just%20business%2C%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20social%20impact.%20A%20chance%20encounter%20with%20Parnika%20Shrimali%2C%20a%20Gurgaon%20resident%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20dispose%20of%20household%20plastic%20waste%20is%20now%20turning%20into%20a%20partnership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finding%20out%20about%20the%20company%2C%20Parnika%2C%20who%20had%20some%20household%20plastic%20waste%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20put%20to%20use%2C%20contacted%20Rishabh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20trash%20and%20it%20was%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20compared%20to%20what%20we%20usually%20work%20with.%20But%20she%20was%20so%20passionate%20about%20not%20throwing%20away%20the%20trash%20mindlessly%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20take%20it%20off%20her%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rishabh.%20Parnika%E2%80%99s%20apartment%20complex%20is%20now%20collaborating%20with%20%E2%80%98Dump%20In%20Bin%E2%80%99%20to%20set%20up%20regular%20plastic%20waste%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20and%20Nitin%20also%20wish%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20ragpickers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%20who%20often%20work%20in%20unsafe%2C%20hazardous%20conditions.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20spoke%20to%20them%20and%20tried%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20whatever%20you%20are%20doing%20in%20collaboration%20with%20different%20contractors%20is%20a%20different%20thing%2C%20but%20we%20would%20like%20to%20work%20with%20you%2C%20give%20you%20a%20proper%20place%20to%20live%20and%20just%20make%20the%20job%20more%20dignified%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rishabh%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C