ote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20album%20is%20a%20genre-defying%20fusion%20of%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20folk%2C%20and%20global%20rhythms%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20widely%20praised%20for%20its%20unique%20sound.%20It%20celebrates%20Indian%20%3Cem%3Eragas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20various%20formats%20and%20incorporates%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20folk%20and%20classical%20percussion%20and%20melodic%20instruments%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%2040%20musicians%20contributed%20to%20this%20record%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F81965%2Fforeigners-indian-classical-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Indian%20sounds%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20context%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20two-week%20production%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20another%20month%20in%20Spain.%20Besides%20Michael%2C%20we%20also%20had%20another%20co-producer%20on%20board%20%E2%80%94%20my%20friend%20and%20accomplished%20percussionist%20Pramat%20Kiran%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8uBJzibp-XI%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20years%20to%20complete%20this%20project%2C%20during%20which%20she%20also%20discovered%20her%20ability%20to%20engage%20in%20songwriting%2C%20specifically%20lyric%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20I%20had%20the%20honour%20of%20working%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20musicians%20who%20are%20like%20heroes%20to%20me%2C%20alongside%20some%20of%20the%20best%20musicians%20from%20Bengaluru.%20The%20music%20on%20this%20album%20comes%20from%20their%20hearts%20and%20exemplifies%20their%20generosity%20of%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20that%20also%20defines%20Varijashree%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20different%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fvarijashree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%2FInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732591800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D382543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Varijashree%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20extraordinary%20singer%2C%20flautist%2C%20and%20composer%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20for%20a%20prestigious%20Grammy%20Award%20this%20year%20for%20her%20contributions%20to%20the%20song%20'A%20Rock%20Somewhere'%2C%20a%20collaboration%20with%20multi-Grammy%20winner%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F382543%2Fvarijashree-venugopal-grammy-award-nomination-a-rock-somehwere-jacob-collier-anoushka-shankar-bengaluru%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20