stematically%20in%20our%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20one%20example%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20in%20our%20village%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311641%2Fdigital-activist-upendra-mahanand-uses-twitter-to-address-pension-ration-card-grievances-in-odisha-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20their%20ration%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20often%20charged%20a%20fee.%20We%20later%20found%20out%20that%20getting%20a%20ration%20card%20should%20be%20free.%20The%20person%20in%20charge%20was%20tricking%20them%20into%20paying%2C%20simply%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%2C%20as%20they%20were%20establishing%20their%20presence%2C%20a%20video%20by%20Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20on%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20garnered%20significant%20attention.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20village%20was%20involved%20in%20making%20that%20film.%20Somehow%2C%20it%20reached%20the%20Collector%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20and%20he%20invited%20us%2C%20asking%20if%20he%20could%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rakesh%20Pawara%20recording%20a%20video%20on%20his%20phone%20which%20will%20be%20shared%20and%20screened%20for%20the%20tribal%20community%20to%20see.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRakesh-during-shoot-2020-1-1732541276.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024