2%20(oxygen%20saturation)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vivek.%20It%20took%20them%20about%20two%20years%20and%20four%20prototypes%20to%20arrive%20at%20their%20final%20product%20%E2%80%98Exam%20D%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintegrated%20with%20our%20VETiNSTANT%20tracker%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVani%20goes%20on%20to%20describe%20the%20motivation%20behind%20Exam%20D%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20need%20for%20a%20user-friendly%20consumer%20interface%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F380268%2Findiegood-sneha-baghrecha-sustainable-eco-friendly-pet-products-india-collaborations-animal-welfare-artisan-crafts-yoda-pfa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct%20for%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20us%20to%20develop%20Exam%20D.%20This%20product%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20features%20a%20graphical%20user%20interface%20that%20simplifies%20customer%20interaction.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20tested%20our%20prototypes%20in%20specific%20markets%20to%20validate%20usage%2C%20gather%20data%2C%20and%20gain%20acceptance%20from%20both%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20use%20Exam%20D%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20VETiNSTANT%20app%20is%20downloaded%20from%20the%20App%20Store%20or%20Play%20Store%2C%20users%20are%20asked%20to%20add%20their%20profile%20details%20followed%20by%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20details%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20are%20one%20or%20many%20and%20what%20species%20they%20belong%20to.%20Users%20can%20buy%20the%20device%20from%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20Exam%20D.%20One%20measures%20temperature%20and%20performs%20heart%2C%20lung%20and%20abdomen%20auscultation%2C%20and%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%206%2C500%20(inclusive%20of%20taxes).%20The%20other%20performs%20all%20the%20above%20but%20also%20gives%20pet%20owners%20readings%20for%20SpO2%20and%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20costs%20Rs%209%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20only%20need%20to%20pair%20the%20app%20and%20device%20the%20first%20time%20when%20you%20buy%20the%20device.%20After%20that%2C%20all%20information%20presented%20in%20an%20executive%20summary%20will%20be%20available%20as%20a%20user%20goes%20through%20the%20prompts%20of%20the%20app%20and%20device%E2%80%99s%20graphic%20user%20interface%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K%20Rajkumar%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Veterinary%20Clinical%20Complex%20at%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20and%20Animal%20Sciences%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20is%20very%20convenient%2C%20especially%20for%20pet%20owners.%20They%20can%20easily%20use%20it%20to%20measure%20their%20pet%E2%80%99s%20temperature%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20lung%20(respiratory)%20sounds%20by%20simply%20placing%20it%20near%20the%20animal.%20The%20recorded%20data%20can%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20a%20veterinarian%20through%20telemedicine%20for%20further%20analysis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exam%20D%20device%20developed%20by%20Vetinstant%20for%20Pet%20Parents%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_394118659_731097555730933_1985252946786160050_n_1080-1732274787-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_3